# diagram outputs — fully regenerable; the pipeline IS what we commit, not its
# output. Keep the dir (via .gitkeep) so the path always resolves; ignore the
# generated SVGs. To commit a specific one as a polished demo: `git add -f
# diagrams/<name>.svg`.
diagrams/*.svg
